title: Fan, ca. 1810
creditline: Bequest of Miss Elizabeth d'Hauteville Kean
description: Pleated fan. Leaf of silk with silk net, embroidered with metallic spangles and stamped metal pieces; sticks of incised horn with applied metallic foil.
